description._content: Description: Resident Comm's Office. Court House and Govt. Secretary's Offices. Location: Solomon Islands ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Showing China Town - Tulagi harbour showing Florida Island in distance. Location: Florida Island, Solomon Islands ------------------------------------------------------ Description: N.S Point. Tulagi Island. W.point Florida or "Gala" Island showing site of proposed causeway. Location: Tulagi Island, Florida Island, Solomon Islands ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Government Secretary's Quarters & mud Hard Tennis Court Location: Solomon Islands ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Residency - Tulagi Location: Tulagi, Solomon Islands ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Batch of Natives, Tulagi, assembles to "Oiga on" as Labourers. Location: Tulagi, Solomon Islands ------------------------------------------------------ Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/641.
